	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65542530"><p>Do you trust your monitor?<br>Some time ago I changed from an Asus smartwatch to a Samsung and my daily stem count dropped 70 per cent, per the smartwatch.<br>In my work group we compared the step count going to and from the coffee shop.<br>The person with the FitBit regularly showed double my step count Apple watch usually showed triple.<br>Scientific Conclusion: Apple makes healthier, right?</p></div>
